1d:["$","p","p-16",{"className":"text-hive-muted leading-relaxed mb-5","children":["The notarized document booklet is submitted to the ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white","children":"Consular Department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of China (MFA)"}]," or its authorized provincial foreign affairs offices for authentication. The MFA verifies the notary's seal and signature, affixing an authentication certificate that certifies the notarization's validity."]}]
